### REST API: Get all books
GET http://localhost:3000/books

### REST API: Get book by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/books/1

### REST API: Create a new book
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Brave New World",
  "author": "Aldous Huxley",
  "year": 1932,
  "genre": "Dystopian",
  "isbn": "978-0060850524"
}

### RPC API: Get book by ID (JSON-RPC 2.0 style)
POST http://localhost:3000/rpc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "getBook",
  "params": { "id": 1 },
  "id": 1
}

### RPC API: Search books
POST http://localhost:3000/rpc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "searchBooks",
  "params": { "query": "1984" },
  "id": 2
}

### GraphQL: Get book details
POST http://localhost:3000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ book(id: 1) { title author year genre } }"
}

### GraphQL: List all books with specific fields
POST http://localhost:3000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ books { id title author } }"
}
